Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所羅門之海波濤洶涌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪拉茲與聯邦兩軍的暗中活動各懷心機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙中形成會合點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到敵作戰計劃書的巴寧格大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲悉了卡多可怕的目地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在此時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他受損的機體化為星塵消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對失去能仰賴的人的宏·浦木來說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉的軍銜章太沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨後是宿命的閱艦式的當日…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60}所羅門的惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,00)\fs40}阿克西斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於聯邦實行地球圈的主權掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能阻止其實現的唯一手段就是迪拉茲的起義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與他們分道揚鑣已有三年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看來彼此的志向仍然一致
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支援罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們反攻的力量終究還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先遣艦隊到何處了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照預定航線
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正向與迪拉茲艦隊的會合點前進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外，搭載MA的調整也沒有延誤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大義…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要在這裏待多少年？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0040,,{\fad(150,00)\fs35}阿克西斯先遣艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.49,0:03:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪拉茲閣下來電
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝對大義的贊同及「星塵」的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖有些微的時間差
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.85,0:03:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但已能直接通信了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是他的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追加電信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位同志，歡迎來地球圈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一樣擅於感人落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0300,,{\fad(150,200)\fs40}金米島·限制海域
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手向金米島方面逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓制住他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我幹這個也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的我會處理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊落三架了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:04:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:05:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是正規軍卻接二連三的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想參加迪拉茲艦隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想與卡多會合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這所羅門之海的某處…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fad(150,340)\fs45}暗礁宙域·金米島中間點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星塵作戰也進入最終階段了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先遣的各艦隊也照預定行事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，是一切的終結嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投下我們全戰力的這個作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將遭受相當大的損失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無力再射出第二支箭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就會墜落了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我瞭解您的心情，閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在萬一的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:06:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我即使中止作戰也必須撤兵嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像屈辱的阿·巴瓦·庫一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0040,,{\fad(150,240)\fs38}所羅門海域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷卻墊圈好了，要把管道接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的，打開回路，快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了要檢查一下10號馬達嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把備用鑽頭拿過來！1-3的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，良好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，能調換嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒見到他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體不適嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想起在這片大海中陣亡的同胞就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾直接跟隨少佐戰鬥的人就只剩我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡留斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到眾多英靈漂流的此地來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我豈非立於眾多的犧牲之上嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是指揮者的宿命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片海還太年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要風平浪靜下來還…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是奔馳而過罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這一刻，大家齊集合於此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該走了嗎？軍曹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊前20分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:07:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請上到MS甲板去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝特大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0-1-0有一不明機體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航道清除
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連吃飯的時間也沒有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿德爾機的補給延誤了2分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我自己掏錢做鴨子料理嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的敵機是第幾架？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到第11架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由於浦木中尉與吉斯少尉的歸艦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝拉拉貝拉管制區防衛減弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他們加快補給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距閱艦式還剩1小時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主力艦艇幾乎都在金米島
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓地球如此空虛真的行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長到現在還認為GUNDAM2號機的目標是賈布羅？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只怕萬一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過幕僚會議想以閱艦式為餌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣做了斷，未免太心急了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右舷彈射器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿德爾機GM Cannon要起飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真行啊，擊落3架…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片海是地獄啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳部進行總線走向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再做一次與定位器的同步檢測
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯少尉沒打開艙門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他睡一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部位強制開放
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天已出擊3次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，現在有點汗臭…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒察覺這裏的氣味嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密閉的軍艦氣味還真重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐氣和體臭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還滲雜著機油味…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知是怎麼了，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？舒服點了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是俘虜嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如所見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正想好好聽他說說迪拉茲艦隊的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了，蒙夏中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說我違反條約嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也該明白現在不是講大道理的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有大志的你們終究會滅亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.27,0:10:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓所羅門的惡夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重現的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0080,,{\fad(200,140)\fs42}地球聯邦軍·金米島·鎮守府
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這金米島如此安寧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪還有ZION軍在徘徊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的警戒網是萬全的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止已擊毀37架敵MS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:11:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢來的話就來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此散漫的攻擊還想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也難怪會有人想通敵了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候去旗艦伯明翰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紳士必須要準時啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次閱艦式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是向太空住民們展現聯邦實力的絕好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儀式的完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就意味著迪拉茲艦隊的敗北吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS要射出了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人員請迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了，祝武運
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷舊的宇宙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.71,0:13:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉多爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊的信號彈怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但、但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本作戰的成否可說是取決於奇襲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點小事就讓敵人識破的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那上天終究是不站在我們這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來只有前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯特爾巡哨區有新的敵影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙夏、浦木、吉斯各機請與貝特機會合，加以迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰鬥要持續到何時？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我逮到卡多為止嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙夏中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航道清除，祝好運
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙歷0079年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是上次的大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對人類而言是最壞的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡過這個困難
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今在事隔三年後又能舉行宇宙一大盛典的閱艦式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為將地球圈的安定與和平具體化之一員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人喜不自勝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來，閱艦式是在地球歷1341年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英法戰爭之際
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由英國的愛德華三世親自觀閱出擊艦隊而肇始的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應當共享的大宇宙之恩惠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若任由部份卑劣之徒蹂躪…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈能容許聯邦說出那種鬼話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別急著赴死，現在要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在手握活著才能得到的那份榮光為止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的性命就托付於我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是對逝去的英靈的褻瀆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在都已經在這裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了掃除聯邦的貪婪之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡留斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航向如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅盤上沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那演說特地為我們引路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我衝入灣內
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了護衛機以外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都照預定進行誘敵擾亂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十、十手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}十手：一種可隔架刀劍的鈍器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是這區域
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主隊在哪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多雖說只有一機，但持有核彈頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mk.82嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那疑似信號彈的報告呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人還會特地鳴槍起跑嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-3及L-7正在迎擊敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪拉茲的目標一定是這儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪拉茲的艦隊才會葬身海底
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去教教他們沒有MS的艦隊會有何下場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受閱艦艇第3群由左舷通過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是警備衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是警備衛星4號
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是Orange3
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭敵機槍攻擊，請求救援
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不堪一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉摩斯巡哨區大量敵MS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在請求增援
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「主賓」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓附近的MS去「歡迎」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝特大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝特大尉聽到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉摩斯巡哨區確認到疑似敵主力部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請急速趕去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G區77
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻前往該地點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好餓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴨子料理煮得如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM2號機…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認到卡多了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前沒有情報
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前還沒有情報
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏還有這麼多所羅門之戰的殘骸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.40,0:20:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此聯邦的傢伙們也難以察知我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片海在哭泣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想對我們訴說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在歡迎我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能聽得到…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木！背後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:21:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙是高手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.22,0:21:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同於之前的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.60,0:22:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是卡多再來這裏的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡留斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裏就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.57,0:22:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行退避行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.46,0:22:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過一陣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.02,0:22:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裏不知瞞過聯邦的耳目出擊過多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此「星塵」就…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動炮台？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發覺了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.70,0:23:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在還有新的敵機？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-0暗礁空域2架
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.10,0:23:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影像傳送過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.55,0:23:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.31,0:23:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多在S-0？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.14,0:23:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裏來得及趕去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧，浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以Full Burnern的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏交給我們，吉斯也去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.50,0:23:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.00,0:23:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有？！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.51,0:24:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再耽擱下去會誤了大事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.51,0:24:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐，這裏交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.64,0:24:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去金米島
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.86,0:24:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！去所羅門
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.08,0:24:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.78,0:24:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下 宏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.93,0:24:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單獨行動很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.16,0:24:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.08,0:24:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等候已久的時刻到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.56,0:24:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了證明許多英靈並非平白喪生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.34,0:24:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的警戒算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.43,0:25:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM2號機？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.27,0:25:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.10,0:25:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金米島的背面
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.54,0:25:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為再次高揭ZION的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.80,0:25:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦為成就「星塵」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.04,0:25:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所羅門啊！我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.41,0:27:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預    告
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.13,0:28:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金米島溢出了光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.22,0:28:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激震的宇宙哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.60,0:28:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐漸實現的迪拉茲的策謀
